\begin{document}$$ Kt/V = \log n\;\left[ {\frac{{C{\text{pre}}}} {{C{\text{eq}}}} - 0.008\;td\; - \frac{{UF}} {{BW}}} \right] $$ \end{document}where td is the dialysis time (h), Cpre and Ceq are, respectively, the predialysis and equilibrated postdialysis urea concentrations, and UF/BW is the ultrafiltrate-to-body weight ratio (L kg−1)
